<description>&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; data-tools=&quot;135&amp;#x7F16;&amp;#x8F91;&amp;#x5668;&quot; data-id=&quot;89172&quot; data-color=&quot;#d82821&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; readability=&quot;14.5&quot;&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;section class=&quot;&quot; readability=&quot;30&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;就在今年7月，当众多留学生好不容易熬过Final等待出成绩时。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

